        Creates a new source model based on the given information
        Parameters:
        type - The type of data flow source
        parameterIdx - The index of the method parameter through which the source value was obtained
        accessPath - The access path describing the exact source object
        gap - The gap from which this flow originated. Null if this flow did not originate from a gap.
